William H. Crawford
United States government official





Also known asWilliam Harris CrawfordbornFebruary 24, 1772Amherst, VirginiadiedSeptember 15, 1834 (aged 62)Elberton, Georgiatitle / officeSenate, United States (1807-1813)political affiliationDemocratic-Republican Party


